      "html": "\n<p><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/tag/Kikobeats/cb2promise.svg?style=flat-square\">\n<a href=\"https://david-dm.org/Kikobeats/cb2promise\"><img src=\"http://img.shields.io/david/Kikobeats/cb2promise.svg?style=flat-square\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://david-dm.org/Kikobeats/cb2promise#info=devDependencies\"><img src=\"http://img.shields.io/david/dev/Kikobeats/cb2promise.svg?style=flat-square\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://www.npmjs.org/package/cb2promise\"><img src=\"http://img.shields.io/npm/dm/cb2promise.svg?style=flat-square\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://paypal.me/kikobeats\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/donate-paypal-blue.svg?style=flat-square\"></a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>It converts from standard NodeJS callback into a ES2015 Promise.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>I use this library across my project for make easy provide API&apos;s that works with callback and promise style.</p>\n<h2>Install</h2>\n<pre>npm install cb2promise --save</pre><h2>Bencharmk</h2>\n<pre>$ node benchmark.js\n\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\"># cb2promise</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\"># 1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8,8,9,10</span>\nok ~2.65 ms (0 s + 2649092 ns)\n\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\"># pify</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\"># 1</span>\nok ~912 &#x3BC;s (0 s + 911730 ns)\n\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\"># es6-promisify</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\"># 1</span>\nok ~967 &#x3BC;s (0 s + 966663 ns)\n\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\"># bluebird</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\"># 1</span>\nok ~3.41 ms (0 s + 3412077 ns)\n\nall benchmarks completed\nok ~7.94 ms (0 s + 7939562 ns)</pre><h2>Usage</h2>\n<pre><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> cb2promise = <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">require</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&apos;cb2promise&apos;</span>)\n\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> callbackFn = <span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> (<span class=\"hljs-params\">message, done</span>) </span>{\n  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> done(<span class=\"hljs-literal\">null</span>, message)\n}\n\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> promise = cb2promise(callbackFn, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&apos;hello world&apos;</span>)\n\npromise().then(<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">console</span>.log)\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">// =&gt; hello world</span></pre><h2>License</h2>\n<p>MIT &#xA9; <a href=\"http://www.kikobeats.com\">Kiko Beats</a></p>\n"
